# Dogfooding artifacts: kit installs into its own project's .claude/
# and .agents/ directories when exercised manually from within ctxr/
# (e.g. during end-to-end verification). Tests use isolated tmpdirs,
# so any .claude/, .agents/, or AGENTS.md in the working copy is
# developer noise, not shipped or tracked.
.claude/
.agents/
AGENTS.md
